uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.tracebuilder

Class ProfileMsnHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.tracebuilder.ProfileMsnHelper

  • public class ProfileMsnHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper class to build and manage the MSn level information for a RawContainer.

    The MSn scans are sorted into a map based on the precursor ion m/z. The map is structured in the following way: msnLevel : parentId : childId : mz, where msn(0) = MS2 (first MSn level)
